Package org.obd Description

The Open Biomedical Ontology Database API

This project consists of a REST service layer and java API for accessing ontology-based annotations in a repository.

Getting started: to see the java API, jump straight to Shard in the org.obd.query package. To see the model, including UML diagrams, proceed to the org.obd.model package. The RESTlet-based web service layer is in org.obd.ws. For an API requirements perspective, see org.obd.test
